high_descs: Move to the island to the left of you
Pick up a fork from the island
Move to the right side of the island
Put the fork in a cup on the island
Pick up the cup from the counter
Move to the sink on the other side of the island
Put the cup in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the end of the room and make a right at the door, then stop when you are beside the kitchen island.
Pick up the fork that is on the kitchen island, between the plate and the salt that is laying on it's side.
Turn and walk towards the door and make a left just before you reach it, then walk go to the kitchen island, between the two chairs.
Place the fork in the Martini glass.
Pick up the Martini glass with the fork inside it.
Walk to your right, then go left, around the kitchen island, to the kitchen sink.
Place the Martini glass with the fork inside it, in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a martini glass containing a fork in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk around the island to face the end.
Pick the fork up off of the island.
Walk to the right then to the left to face the island.
Place the fork in the martini glass on the counter.
Pick the martini glass up off of the counter.
Move to the right and then to the left to face the sink.
Place the martini glass in to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the fork in the martini glass in to the sink.
